headline: TKO Announces $1 Billion in Share Repurchases
summary: NEW YORK, September 15, 2025--TKO Group Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: TKO) ("TKO" or the "Company"), a premium sports and entertainment company, today announced that it has entered into an accelerated share repurchase agreement (the "ASR Agreement") to repurchase $800 million of its outstanding Class A common stock.
